# Automatic Detection of Moral Values in Research Papers

## Overview
This project presents an automated system for detecting moral and ethical values in AI and Machine Learning research papers using transformer-based NLP models.

---

## Dataset
- **Seed papers:** 99 manually annotated publications
- **All papers:** 250+ DBLP conference papers
- PDFs are automatically processed and converted into JSON files.

---

## Methodology
1. PDF text extraction
2. Zero-shot moral value detection
3. Supervised multi-label classification (RoBERTa)
4. IR-style theme mapping
5. Evaluation and analysis

